@aday I now have a somewhat working image editing UI for the crop view. What diverges from the original mockups is that I added an "apply" button. I think we need something like this for the cropping. The main use case would be to do a finer crop adjustment after the first rough crop. For that, the crop has to be applied in some way. Mobile apps do stuff like automatically applying the crop after a second, but I always struggled with that so I don't want to use it here.

I also wonder if we maybe want the undo buttons in every view.

@jimmac I just used whatever icons I found for that view. Let me know if there are better icons that I should use.

Generally, feedback is welcome. The goal for now was to get something working as a first step.

